        {
            "title": "中資公司香港配股唯一買家 Infini高調吃進賺得盆滿缽滿",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 一家香港投資公司在飆升的市場中通過高調配股搶購中國股票，短期內就實現了大量獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由Tony Chin創立的多策略投資公司Infini Capital在認購軟件供應商微盟周三的定向增發後，一天內就錄得約2.3億港元（3000 萬美元）獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周早些時候，它對協鑫科技的投資三天內就斬獲近10億港元，因此間該股上漲了8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯總的數據顯示，Infini在過去三個月中至少完成了五筆此類交易，其目標主要是科技公司，包括商湯科技和第四範式。該基金以約4%至9%的折讓價買入這些股票。假設它繼續持有，配售產生的賬面利潤就超過了30億港元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6042adcf-6ded-359e-a12d-02fb38bf1712-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S_Jrq3BAjt5IAXpIi8VR6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b1d415d0d1c761889f8cb3059a2a7bc1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Infini的投資者關係團隊暫未回覆通過電子郵件發送的評論請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國股票的火爆行情推動了配股後的強勁回報。人工智能開發商商湯科技的股價今年已飆升76%，而第四範式則上漲了26%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S0U5dSu27f0bHxa6knevsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8352347295dd27d917af87a229f96233\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Infini Emerges as Sole Buyer in String of China Share Placements</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%85%8D%E8%82%A1%E5%94%AF-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6-infini%E9%AB%98%E8%AA%BF%E5%90%83%E9%80%B2%E8%B3%BA%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%86%E6%BB%BF%E7%BC%BD%E6%BB%BF-171612618.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 09:35:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國終止查谷歌 聚焦監管輝達",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國終止查谷歌 聚焦監管輝達\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ttyYNjTibp6OX9rK4W1dDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/73e2b750-91c8-11f0-beab-46c4aec916f0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國終止查谷歌 聚焦監管輝達</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
